A simple HTML5 slideshow gallery using figure/img/figcaption
Still under developement. 

Dependencies: Ender.js (see http://enderjs.com for instructions on build and license)

TO-DO:
- play/pause methods
- optionally add secondary navigation (prev/next arrows, 1/2/3... bullets)
- Reusable object to generate different instances in one page
- Chain methods to $
- encapsulation according to Bridge API + NPM

